---

## 3. Templates & Configurations — CC0 1.0

**Applies to:** `.github/` templates, GitHub configurations

### CC0 1.0 Universal (Public Domain Dedication)

The person who associated a work with this deed has dedicated the work to the 
public domain by waiving all of his or her rights to the work worldwide under 
copyright law, including all related and neighboring rights, to the extent 
allowed by law.

Full license text: https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/legalcode

---

## Contributor Agreement | 贡献者协议

By submitting contributions to this repository, you agree that:

1. Your documentation contributions will be licensed under **CC BY-NC-ND 4.0**
2. Your code contributions will be licensed under **MIT License**
3. You will receive appropriate **contributor attribution** in published versions

通过向本仓库提交贡献，您同意：

1. 您的文档贡献将遵循 **CC BY-NC-ND 4.0** 协议
2. 您的代码贡献将遵循 **MIT 许可证**
3. 您将在发布版本中获得相应的**贡献者署名**

